    "source_url": "https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/google-search",
    "comment": "`generateContent` with `tools: [{google_search: {}}]` \u2014 model decides when to search and returns synthesized text plus `groundingMetadata` sources (use `answer=true` in anysearch). Default model `gemini-2.5-flash` via `provider_config.gemini.model`."
  },
  "notes": "Native SDK package: google-genai."
